sourcesContent: import React from 'react'; import { BrowserRouter as Router, Routes, Route } from 'react-router-dom'; import Navbar from './components/Navbar'; import Home from './pages/Home'; import Login from './pages/Login'; import Register from './pages/Register'; import RequestForm from './pages/RequestForm'; import ProtectedRoute from './components/ProtectedRoute'; import Dashboard from './pages/Dashboard'; export default function App(){ return (<Router><Navbar /><main className='container'><Routes><Route path='/' element={<Home/>} /><Route path='/login' element={<Login/>} /><Route path='/register' element={<Register/>} /><Route path='/request' element={<ProtectedRoute><RequestForm/></ProtectedRoute>} /><Route path='/dashboard' element={<ProtectedRoute><Dashboard/></ProtectedRoute>} /></Routes></main></Router>); }
